Sentencas: This paper describes the low temperature operation of a solid oxide fuel cell using cubic stabilized zirconia in the ZrO2-Sc2O3-Al2O3 system as an electrolyte.
Titulo: LOW-TEMPERATURE OPERATION OF SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL WITH A ZRO2-SC2O3-AL2O3 SYSTEM ELECTROLYTE

Sentencas: The hydrogen-oxygen fuel cell was fabricated by using La0.8Sr0.2MnO3 as the cathode material and Ni-YSZ as the anode material.
Titulo: LOW-TEMPERATURE OPERATION OF SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL WITH A ZRO2-SC2O3-AL2O3 SYSTEM ELECTROLYTE

Sentencas: The maximum power density is 0.63 W/cm(2) at 800 degrees C and 1.0 W/cm(2) at 880 degrees C.
Titulo: LOW-TEMPERATURE OPERATION OF SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL WITH A ZRO2-SC2O3-AL2O3 SYSTEM ELECTROLYTE

Sentencas: The current-voltage performance of this fuel cell suggests that the present electrolyte is a good candidate for fuel cells operating in the temperature range between 800 and 900 degrees C.
Titulo: LOW-TEMPERATURE OPERATION OF SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELL WITH A ZRO2-SC2O3-AL2O3 SYSTEM ELECTROLYTE
